# bivario
Python library for plotting bivariate choropleth maps in Matplotlib, Folium and Lonboard.

<p align="center">
  <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RaczeQ/bivario/main/images/bivario_logo.png" width="500"><br/>
</p>

